    <p>Welcome... to the Shiloh Missionary Baptist Church in Anchorage, Alaska! We provide a Children's Ministry called Seeds of Promise. The primary purpose of this ministry is to prepare children for a lifetime of devotion to Jesus Christ.</p>
    <p>Your participation is encouraged. It takes a combined effort to operate our Nursery, Preschool, and Elementary Ministries. Together, we will build a firm spiritual foundation for your children.</p>
    <p>If you are interested in becoming a team member or have questions concerning the Children's Ministry, please contact Mrs. Donna King, Mrs. Toni Gamble, or any of the members of the Children's Ministry staff. Please click one of the logos below to find out more about our Seeds of Promise Children's Ministry.</p>
